{"tid":2034412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"98歲賭王何鴻燊傳病危　家人趕往醫院","createTime":"2020-05-25T08:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T09:02:47.000Z","uid":10540,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"892fccddc402d22b1d03d56eaafbbfeba0804c5d","tid":2034412,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/photo/bkn-20200525155215453-0525_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200525155353\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200525155215453-0525_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200525155353&h=1d1b2e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年98歲賭王何鴻燊近年健康情況欠佳，長期住院休養，四房家人每日輪流往醫院照顧，去年2月曾突然傳出他病況轉差，需在醫院深切治療部（ICU）留醫。今日再有消息指何鴻燊病危，情況不樂觀，醫院已陸續通知家人到醫院留守。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525155215453-0525_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1l8AToVwhCSSlHmUp-3nUpVgfkl-tQiyEulrdiwOWN6E82ql9yv0_OISg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fbkn-20200525155215453-0525_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1l8AToVwhCSSlHmUp-3nUpVgfkl-tQiyEulrdiwOWN6E82ql9yv0_OISg&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3gpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=adbfcaff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525155215453-0525_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1l8AToVwhCSSlHmUp-3nUpVgfkl-tQiyEulrdiwOWN6E82ql9yv0_OISg</a>"},{"pid":"726921de4ec7b5457744cf83a0a2ac5da9989aaa","tid":2034412,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"fdb4d42e8a671c7032236bfa09680ffb3917b054","tid":2034412,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"成日見佢d prescription<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115592165ad8e1442fcbc01cabaf4075340347ca","tid":2034412,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"